{"tid":2138584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港自建亞博治療中心被大陸邀功 彭博疑照抄fake news捱轟","createTime":"2020-08-03T16:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T04:01:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4269fc2e1a4404ce4ff2230bc73cf0b2a3aa46b0","tid":2138584,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/WG5ZJGWSV3LECIALQZ5YNVVBZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FWG5ZJGWSV3LECIALQZ5YNVVBZY%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0OyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=d2de29d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FWG5ZJGWSV3LECIALQZ5YNVVBZY%2F&h=117331d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/WG5ZJGWSV3LECIALQZ5YNVVBZY/</a><br />\n<br />\n8月1日啟用嘅機場亞洲博覽館「社區治療設施」，明明係醫管局一手一腳改建，居然俾大陸邀功，辣㷫好多人。事關大陸衞生健康委話，派6個武漢專家嚟香港「協助建方艙」，為改建亞博「提供設計、營運及管理經驗」喎。但你人都未到，個設施已經正式啟用，仲點樣「協助建」呢？之前被爆親中嘅彭博通訊社，竟然完全照抄衞健委同央視嘅所謂「報道」唔fact check，仲大字標題話「中國幫香港起臨時醫院（China to Help Hong Kong Build Mobile Hospital）」，激到大批網民去佢Facebook鬧爆佢寫fake news。"},{"pid":"a4565cfafbfff736bf62df53d0528b81ea4f9ba1","tid":2138584,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372f31856ddc9413e0fcfb0937b9a0da539a693d","tid":2138584,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src